{
  "stem": "1704.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 257.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The trains-- the buses, the trains, everything, one day, and then just-- the Germans just picked up a lot of people, and shot them, and it was finished.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's still remembered every year as the February Strike.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They've got a big statue in, in the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's still remembered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they wanted to help, but they couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, everybody says, oh, the Dutch were so good, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For every good one, there were two bad ones, or maybe the other way around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were a lot of bad ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And very, very many very good ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that they would place-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were-- as soon as people were taken out of their houses to be sent to the camps, there used to come a big furniture van, Dutch people, and emptied the house, went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bad, very bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was the reason why my fiance was picked up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a big furniture van opposite this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came to say goodbye to me, because he went to a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he didn't wear a star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they saw me coming in the street, he came up to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wore a star.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't, and those Dutch people from the furniture van picked him out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how he was caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only met him in June, I think, and in September he went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the short time, we met for such a lot, it, it was like years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just in the street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I went out with some girlfriends, and wearing the star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was by himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started talking to us with-- normally.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
